<% provide(:title, "About") %>

    <!-- Lead -->

    <section class="row-alt">
      <div class="lead container">
        <h1><%= full_title(yield(:title), true) %> - Code Island</h1>
        <p>Since 2014</p>
      </div>
    </section>

     <section class="row">
      <div class="grid">
          <div class="col-2-3">
		      <p>
		        Code Island is the official <a href="http://codeforamerica.org/">Code for America</a> brigade in Rhode Island. We are an all-volunteer organization of people looking to improve our community through technology.
		      </p>
		      <p>
		        As a general rule, Code Island holds a <a href="http://www.meetup.com/Rhode-Island-Code-for-America-Brigade/">meetup</a> the first and third Tuesday of every month at 6pm at <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/10+Davol+Square,+Providence,+RI+02903/@41.824152,-71.4398007,13z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x89e4456a8646dbf1:0x2259e0f433c149cf?hl=en">Brown Universityâ€™s TRI Lab at 10 Davol Square</a>. Our meetups are free and open to anyone who wants to contribute to our work.
		      </p>
		      <p>Stay in Touch</p>
		      <ul>
            	  <li>Check out our projects over on our <%= link_to image_tag("Social/github.png", class: "twitter", alt: "GitHub") + " Github repository", "https://github.com/codeisland/" %></li>
            	  <li>Follow us <%= link_to image_tag("Social/twitter.png", class: "twitter", alt: "@code_island") + " @Code_island", "http://www.twitter.com/code_island" %> on Twitter</li>
            	  <li>Send us <%= link_to image_tag("Social/e-mail.png", class: "twitter", alt: "Email") + " info", "mailto:info@code-island.org" %> on old-fashion Email</li>
            	  <li>Like us <%= link_to image_tag("Social/facebook.png", class: "twitter", alt: "Facebook") + " Code Island Brigade", "https://www.facebook.com/codeislandbrigade" %></li>
            	  <li>Join our <%= link_to image_tag("Social/google.png", class: "twitter", alt: "Google+") + "Google+ community", "https://plus.google.com/u/0/communities/112228497378493874687" %></li>
		      </ul>
          </div>
      </div>
    </section>
